{{Top|leg}}
A '''yu'nar''' was a ruling tribunal of the [[Trianii/Legends|Trianii]] society. The tribunals were all [[Gender/Legends|female]], reflecting the matriarchal culture of the Trianii. Over the centuries, the yu'nars formed a strong religious moral code. Spirituality permeated trade, industry, and every aspect of Trianii society.

